S.FORM: George Blaney nalecuhan i Jersey City, New Jersey, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. George Blaney i 1961 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 4 ku uwac atu silsil 33, namapili' tu nu New York Knicks putiput. tatama, nalecuhan i11 a bulad 12 a demiad, 1939 a mihcan, George Blaney, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
